rComments: Colin keeps things interesting in lecture, but the class itself was tough.  There were 3 exams and a final, and 11 quizzes (10 of which composed an exam's worth of points).  There were always at least 1 or 2 questions on each exam that were impossible unless you know Calc well--the final had 2 of them (worth 20 points each on a 200 point final)!
